      "contentHtml": "<p>For additional information about this major, please visit <a href=\"https://ethnicstudies.ucr.edu/ethnic-studies/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Ethnic Studies Studies</a>. </p><p>For information about the UC Transfer Admission Guarantee (TAG) program, please visit <a href=\"https://admission.universityofcalifornia.edu/admission-requirements/transfer-requirements/uc-transfer-programs/transfer-admission-guarantee-tag.html\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Transfer Admission Guarantee</a>.</p>"
